## 🚀 Key Features

### **AI Video Generation**
- Text-to-video powered by Kling Video AI
- Cinematic quality output
- Multiple style options (cinematic, dramatic, documentary, etc.)
- Custom duration and aspect ratios
- "Surprise Me" random prompt generator

### **Music & Audio**
- Professional royalty-free music library
- Pre-made music templates (organized by mood/genre)
- Religious and spiritual music collection
- Custom music upload
- Audio editing and mixing

### **Content Creation Tools**
- Picture-to-video conversion
- Video upload and management
- CapCut-style effects and transitions
- Custom branding and watermarks
- Batch video generation

### **Sharing & Distribution**
- One-click export to all platforms
- Optimized formats for each platform
- Direct sharing to social media
- Scheduled posting
- Analytics tracking per platform

### **Creator Dashboard**
- Real-time video statistics
- Performance analytics
- Earnings tracking
- Creator leaderboard
- Revenue sharing (30% commission)

### **Security & Compliance**
- Enterprise-grade encryption (AES-256)
- GDPR and CCPA compliant
- Video DRM protection
- Audit logging
- Secure authentication (JWT + OAuth)

